**What This Means:**
- The FAST (instant) DDA took 8.76 milliseconds
- The SLOW (animated) DDA took 125.43 milliseconds
- That's **14.31 times slower**—but you get to see every step!
- The animated version used **9.9% more CPU** due to screen refreshes

